tags.name: The Beanhill Tinman
tags.wheelchair:description: - Level paved path to wheelchair accessible basketball court. -Fitness stations and gazebo semi-accessible to those who can transfer and/or stand for short periods. -Back half of park is grass with narrow rocky path to Beanhill Tinman & kids playground.

Level access to basketball court and trim trail. Pavement around perimeter of playground. Swings and super seesaw in middle of grass on slight incline. Wifi gazebo has step, is too small to accommodate wheelchair.
